Package management

Class Manager

java.lang.Object
management.Staff
management.Manager
All Implemented Interfaces:
IXlsxSerializable
public class Manager extends Staff
Manager class represents an administrative user with more exclusive privileges than Staff. This class extends the Staff class and provides methods for administrative actions to manage Menus within their own Branch.
